OL,3,CKent prison 'repurposed' to house
OL,4,Cexpected influx of riot criminals
OL,6,FA former young offender institution in
OL,7,FKent is to be 'repurposed' as an adult
OL,8,Fprison in the wake of riots across the
OL,9,Fcountry, the government has announced.
OL,11,FHMP Cookham Wood will reopen 'in the
OL,12,Fcoming weeks' as part of a plan to
OL,13,Furgently create an additional 500
OL,14,Fprison places across England.
OL,16,FThe facility was earmarked for closure
OL,17,Fto juveniles in March after a series
OL,18,Fof damning inspection reports led to a
OL,19,Fformal warning over safety from the
OL,20,Fprisons watchdog.
