OL,3,CKent prison 'repurposed' to house
OL,4,Cexpected influx of riot criminals
OL,6,FITV News understands that existing
OL,7,Fplans to convert the jail in Rochester
OL,8,Fto hold adult inmates have been
OL,9,Fbrought forward following days of
OL,10,Fserious violence and disorder in
OL,11,FEnglish towns and cities.
OL,13,FCourts Minister Heidi Alexander said:
OL,14,F"We will make sure that all parts of
OL,15,Fthe criminal justice system, whether
OL,16,Fthat's the courts or the prisons, can
OL,17,Feffectively dispense justice so that
OL,18,Fthe individuals who are committing
OL,19,Fthese heinous acts will face the full
OL,20,Fforce of the law."
