OL,3,CKent prison 'repurposed' to house
OL,4,Cexpected influx of riot criminals
OL,6,FCookham Wood, in the village of
OL,7,FBorstal near Rochester, was already
OL,8,Fdue to reopen for adults this summer
OL,9,Fbut scores of new cells will now
OL,10,Fbecome available for use within weeks,
OL,11,Faccording to a Ministry of Justice
OL,12,Fsource.
OL,14,FLocal Labour MP Lauren Edwards, who
OL,15,Frepresents Rochester and Strood, told
OL,16,FITV News she "completely welcomes" the
OL,17,F"accelerated plans" for Cookham Wood.
OL,19,FDespite these contingency measures,
OL,20,FEngland's prison estate is expected to
OL,21,Freach capacity again in September.
