OL,4,Cexpected influx of riot criminals
OL,6,FLord Chancellor and Justice Secretary,
OL,7,FShabana Mahmood, said: "The far-right
OL,8,Fthuggery we have witnessed on our
OL,9,Fstreets is completely unacceptable and
OL,10,Fcontrary to the British notion of rule
OL,11,Fof law.
OL,13,F"My message to anyone who chooses to
OL,14,Ftake part in this violence is simple.
OL,15,FThe police, courts and prisons stand
OL,16,Fready and you will face the
OL,17,Fconsequences of these appalling acts."
