OL,6,FThere are plans to hold disorder
OL,7,Fsuspects in police custody for longer
OL,8,Fperiods to manage the short term
OL,9,Finflux of people being held on remand,
OL,10,Fwhile awaiting trial or sentencing.
OL,12,FOther contingency plans include
OL,13,Fextending the working hours of
OL,14,Fmagistrates' courts to process riot
OL,15,Fsuspects, if required.
